{"content": "<p><em>Artist, explorer, convivial mystic.</em><br /><a href=\"https://twitter.com/WeseeThisnow\">@WeSeeThisNow.eth</a> launched their entrancing genesis collection on October 30th 2021...and ever since then it has continued to build at a steady pace. Ok let's get in to the details, because a lot of thought has gone into the creation of this collection. </p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Today I launched my first collection of NFTs. Eighty 1/1, released in twenty groups of four, every few days. <a href=\"https://t.co/xRb5XKBD8H\">https://t.co/xRb5XKBD8H</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/k1yd6qqETi\">pic.twitter.com/k1yd6qqETi</a></p>&mdash; WeseeThisnow.eth (@WeseeThisnow) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/WeseeThisnow/status/1454191976165818371?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">October 29, 2021</a></blockquote><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></figure><h3 id=\"greatest-city-in-the-whirled-collection\">Greatest City in the Whirled Collection</h3><p>First, there is a total of 80 1/1 NFT manipulated photographs each with its own personal reflection included by @WeSeeThisNow. </p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/Swimming-In-Stone.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"600\" height=\"690\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/Swimming-In-Stone.jpg 600w\"><figcaption><a href=\"https://opensea.io/assets/0x495f947276749ce646f68ac8c248420045cb7b5e/33973249879990965083896500139954924904838592705958356341288020574438737051649\">Swimming in Stone</a> by @WeSeeThisNow on OpenSea marketplace</figcaption></figure><p>Accompanying the 'Swiming in Stone' artwork is a reflection by the artist that brings their own fingerprint to bear on the elliptical photographic layers. </p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/Screen-Shot-2021-11-06-at-4.33.01-PM-1200x518.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"864\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/1_Screen-Shot-2021-11-06-at-4.33.01-PM.png 600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/2_Screen-Shot-2021-11-06-at-4.33.01-PM.png 1000w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/Screen-Shot-2021-11-06-at-4.33.01-PM.png 1600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/Screen-Shot-2021-11-06-at-4.33.01-PM-1200x518.png 2200w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption>Personal reflection for Swimming in Stone by @WeSeeThisNow</figcaption></figure><p>Memories, Dreams and Reflections draws you into the centre of its vortex before revealing a lattice ripple of spades that intersect our eyes.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2021/11/unnamed-34.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"2500\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/unnamed-34.jpg 600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/1_unnamed-34-640x800.jpg 1000w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/2_unnamed-34-640x800.jpg 1600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/3_unnamed-34-640x800.jpg 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption><a href=\"https://opensea.io/assets/0x495f947276749ce646f68ac8c248420045cb7b5e/33973249879990965083896500139954924904838592705958356341288020570040690540545\">Memories, Dreams, Reflections</a> on OpenSea</figcaption></figure><p>Memories, Dreams and Reflections is an abstraction making it difficult to fathom where the buildings meet. Where is the sky introduced? ...and how an earth the cyclical patterns are so seamlessly handshaking with each other. A looot of effort has gone in to the technicals of each image, and those technicals are shared with us. As the collection evolves, these % will change too. </p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/Screen-Shot-2021-11-06-at-4.38.53-PM.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"822\" height=\"486\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/1_Screen-Shot-2021-11-06-at-4.38.53-PM.png 600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/Screen-Shot-2021-11-06-at-4.38.53-PM.png 822w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><p>The first collection starts at 0.1 eth and each quad (group of four) is then introduced at a slightly higher price. The first four are your best bet on the genesis collection of @WeSeeThisNow.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/Screen-Shot-2021-11-06-at-4.42.54-PM-1200x343.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1908\" height=\"546\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/1_Screen-Shot-2021-11-06-at-4.42.54-PM.png 600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/2_Screen-Shot-2021-11-06-at-4.42.54-PM.png 1000w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/3_Screen-Shot-2021-11-06-at-4.42.54-PM-1200x344.png 1600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/Screen-Shot-2021-11-06-at-4.42.54-PM-1200x343.png 1908w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><p>You can ask questions about the art process and follow along as new drops are announced by turning on notifications on @WeSeeThisNow's Twitter profile. </p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/Screen-Shot-2021-11-06-at-4.49.36-PM-1170x800.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1202\" height=\"822\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/1_Screen-Shot-2021-11-06-at-4.49.36-PM.png 600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/2_Screen-Shot-2021-11-06-at-4.49.36-PM.png 1000w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/Screen-Shot-2021-11-06-at-4.49.36-PM-1170x800.png 1202w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><hr /><p><strong><a href=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/#/portal/signup\">Subscribe to MintFace</a> and receive new artist features by email.</strong></p><p>If this article has made you curious about getting started with digital art, we also run the <a href=\"https://maven.com/cache/nft-digital-artist-economy\">Digital Artist Economy workshop</a> helping artists create their first digital art through a <a href=\"https://maven.com/cache/nft-digital-artist-economy\">three week programme.</a> Share it with an artist you'd like to see on an NFT marketplace.</p><p><strong>MintFace surfaces great artists and artworks so you don't have to. </strong></p><p><em>Enjoying MintFace? Subscribe for $9 per month.</em></p><p></p>"}